Name: athena-synctree
Summary: An Athena tool to synchronize directory trees
License: MIT
Group: Applications/File

%description
Synctree intelligently copies one directory tree to another, according
to a set of rules files found in both the source and destination
directory trees.  synctree allows files to copied from the source to
the destination, establish sym- bolic links on the destination tree,
and allows commands to be executed when files are updated.

